name: Reservas
query: SELECT name as "N. Reserva",booked_by as "Feita por",check_in as "Data Entrada",check_out as "Data Saida",numero_quarto as "Quarto N.", numero_cliente as "Nome do Cliente", reservation_status as "Status", pay_advance as "Pago em Avanco" FROM tabRESERVAS WHERE(reservation_status LIKE "Ativo" OR "Novo");
